IMAPAccount disroot
Host disroot.org
User uspro@disroot.org
PassCmd "cat emailpwds.txt | tail -n1"
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore disroot-remote
Account disroot

MaildirStore disroot-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/disroot/
Inbox ~/.mail/disroot/inbox

Channel disroot
Master :disroot-remote:
Slave :disroot-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
Sync pull
Expunge none
